umber of employees  june  website wwwgloworldcom globacom limited or glo is a nigerian multinational telecommunications company headquartered in lagos glo is a privately owned telecommunications carrier that started operations on  august  it currently operates in four countries in west africa namely nigeria republic of benin ghana and côte divoire as of june  the company has employed more than  people worldwide contents  overview  ownership  strategic business units  glo mobile  glo gateway  broadband access  glo  submarine cable  by country  history  sponsorships  references  external links overviewedit glo has an estimate of over  million subscribers april  of which  million are internet subscribers and it is a  percent nigerian owned company glo built an  million highcapacity fibreoptic cable known as glo a submarine cable from the united kingdom to nigeria ownershipedit glo is privately owned by the mike adenuga group which also consists of etb now merged with the sterling bank conoil plc a petroleum marketing company and conoil producing a crude exploration company strategic business unitsedit glo mobileedit glo mobile a subsidiary of glo is glo’s mobile network unit in the first year of operation it had one million subscribers in over  towns in nigeria and over  billion naira in revenues glo mobile has now spread to other african countries namely benin and ghana glo gatewayedit glo gateway a subsidiary of glo is glo’s international wholesale voice and data exchange trading business unit due to an expansion program which took place in  glo gateway nowyear needed covers  countries under its roaming services and it is currently connected to  networks  also saw growth in glo’s data roaming for mobile phones laptops and blackberry handsets which has now spread to  networks in  countries this now gives glo the largest roaming coverage for voice and data in africa glo gateway recently acquired a license in côte divoire broadband accessedit as a part of glo’s service offering glo broad access will be improved by the laying of the fibre optic cable for the metro ring which is progressing steadilycitation needed the glo broad access was launched on the th of november  glo broad access offers landline telephones broadband internet and video all on a single digital wire line glo  submarine cableedit glo is the first successful submarine cable from the united kingdom to nigeria and glo is the first individual african company to embark on such a project glo has the potential to provide high speed internet services faster more reliable and cheaper telecom services glo will potentially facilitate foreign investment and employment opportunities especially to africans the  km long cable originates from bude in the uk and is laid from this origin to alpha beach in lagos where it will have its landing station glo will also improve teleconferencing distance learning disaster recovery and telemedicine among several other benefits for nigerians and the people of west africa by countryedit in august  glo mobile was launched in nigeria glo mobile introduced lower tariffs pay per second billing and alongside other value added services although glo mobile was the fourth gsm operator to launch in nigeria within seven years of the companys operation its subscriber base has grown to over  million in june  glo mobile was launched in benin glo mobile showed unprecedented growth through the sale of  sim cards in the first ten days of operation glo mobile offered per second billing which charges subscribers for the exact airtime used they also offered other value added services such as mms multimedia messaging service glo magic plus news and information vehicle tracking musical ringback tones and mobile banking in may  glo acquired an operating license through its glo mobile division in ghana and plans to capture  of the current  million subscriber market within  months of launch they plan on achieving this goal by launching with bundled voice and internet services for ghana and through specifically targeting ‘unserviced’ areas outside ghana’s two major cities accra and kumasi glo mobile was set to launch in ghana the first quarter of  this has however been postponed to the third quarter of  and again to  in january  glo ghana opened the reserve your number campaign but still without opening the network on april   glo launched the submarine optical fiber glo one part of its maiden operation in ghana to usher in another major player in the ghana telecommunication industry in october  glo acquired submarine cable landing rights and international gateway services in côte divoire historyedit in  glo mobile introduced the glo fleet manager which is a vehicle tracking solution glo fleet manager helps transportersfleet operators manage their fleet they also introduced the glo mobile internet service which provides subscribers with access to internet sites which have been customized for mobile phone browsing in  glo mobile introduced blackberry glo started the sponsorship of the confederation of african football african player of the year award the company also started the sponsorship of glo lagos international half marathon in  glo mobile launched blackberry prepaid services which gives subscribers options to pay daily weekly or monthly for the service blackberry prepaid service gives subscribers free yahoo mail access and free blackberry messenger the company also launched g high speed internet services through the sale of its g modem glo mobile g network is available in lagos abuja benin and portharcourt sponsorshipsedit glo sponsors sports events nigerian supporters in gloshirts at  fifa u womens world cup in nigeria glo sponsored until  the nigerian premier league nigerian national football teams nigeria football federation nff glo lagos international half marathon glo people police marathon eyo festival ojude oba festival eleghe festival and the confederation of african football african player of the year award in benin glo sponsors the fitheb and caf african player of the year award in ghana glo sponsors the glo ghana premier league the ghana national football teams and the caf african player of the year award in november  glo became an official sponsor of football club manchester united the sponsorship also includes young players from benin ghana and nigeria going to manchester to train with the club referencesedit  nkanga efem benin glo launches network in country today all africa  june   bello muhammed nigerian communications commission retrieved  december    a b globacom leads africa middle east mobile market with m subscribers it news africa  may  accessed  august   it news africa glo one submarine cable debuts in lagos it news africa  september  accessed  august   glo makes test call telegeography  december  accessed  august   globacom may acquire nitel daily champion  september  accessed  august   nkanga efem benin glo launches network in country today all africa  june  accessed  august   a b c nweke remmy ereadiness nigeria ranks  daily champion  june  accessed  september   glo one submarine cable debuts in lagos it news  september  accessed  november   glo  submarine cable lands in lagos vanguard  september  accessed  november   eribake akintayo  september  glo  submarine cable lands in lagos retrieved  december    nigeria glo  berths in accra  september  retrieved  december  – via allafrica   the nation newspaper nigeria  read latest nigeria news retrieved  december    nkanga efem  september  nigeria globacom is  percent nigerian company  jameel retrieved  december  – via allafrica   cellularnews retrieved  december    it edge news  it edge news  africa glo congratulates africa on ghanas victory  october  retrieved  december  – via allafrica   glo lagos marathon retrieved  december    nigeria glo people police marathon  fighting crime through sports  april  retrieved  december  – via allafrica   ojudeoba festival retrieved  december    this day online  hotel luggage 